<div class="px-4 py-5" id="features">
  <h1 class="pb-2 border-bottom display-5 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3">Benefits</h1>
  <div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">
    <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
      <div class="icon-square bg-light text-dark flex-shrink-0 me-3">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-trophy-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
          <path d="M2.5.5A.5.5 0 0 1 3 0h10a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5c0 .538-.012 1.05-.034 1.536a3 3 0 1 1-1.133 5.89c-.79 1.865-1.878 2.777-2.833 3.011v2.173l1.425.356c.194.048.377.135.537.255L13.3 15.1a.5.5 0 0 1-.3.9H3a.5.5 0 0 1-.3-.9l1.838-1.379c.16-.12.343-.207.537-.255L6.5 13.11v-2.173c-.955-.234-2.043-1.146-2.833-3.012a3 3 0 1 1-1.132-5.89A33.076 33.076 0 0 1 2.5.5zm.099 2.54a2 2 0 0 0 .72 3.935c-.333-1.05-.588-2.346-.72-3.935zm10.083 3.935a2 2 0 0 0 .72-3.935c-.133 1.59-.388 2.885-.72 3.935z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Workout</h2>
        <p>Use the workouts generator to create and save your own workouts. Plan ahead of your gym visit or copy an existing public workout to your profile.</p>
        <%= link_to "Create a workout", new_workout_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
      <div class="icon-square bg-light text-dark flex-shrink-0 me-3">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-people" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
          <path d="M15 14s1 0 1-1-1-4-5-4-5 3-5 4 1 1 1 1h8zm-7.978-1A.261.261 0 0 1 7 12.996c.001-.264.167-1.03.76-1.72C8.312 10.629 9.282 10 11 10c1.717 0 2.687.63 3.24 1.276.593.69.758 1.457.76 1.72l-.008.002a.274.274 0 0 1-.014.002H7.022zM11 7a2 2 0 1 0 0-4 2 2 0 0 0 0 4zm3-2a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0zM6.936 9.28a5.88 5.88 0 0 0-1.23-.247A7.35 7.35 0 0 0 5 9c-4 0-5 3-5 4 0 .667.333 1 1 1h4.216A2.238 2.238 0 0 1 5 13c0-1.01.377-2.042 1.09-2.904.243-.294.526-.569.846-.816zM4.92 10A5.493 5.493 0 0 0 4 13H1c0-.26.164-1.03.76-1.724.545-.636 1.492-1.256 3.16-1.275zM1.5 5.5a3 3 0 1 1 6 0 3 3 0 0 1-6 0zm3-2a2 2 0 1 0 0 4 2 2 0 0 0 0-4z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Community</h2>
        <p>Join a community of fitness enthusiats. Motivate others and create unique and cool content. Choose from publicly available exercises or create your own and share them.</p>
        <%= link_to "Create an exercise", new_exercise_path, "data-controller": "turbo", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
      <div class="icon-square bg-light text-dark flex-shrink-0 me-3">
        <%# <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="#tools"/></svg> %>
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height="1em" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-bootstrap-reboot" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
          <path d="M1.161 8a6.84 6.84 0 1 0 6.842-6.84.58.58 0 1 1 0-1.16 8 8 0 1 1-6.556 3.412l-.663-.577a.58.58 0 0 1 .227-.997l2.52-.69a.58.58 0 0 1 .728.633l-.332 2.592a.58.58 0 0 1-.956.364l-.643-.56A6.812 6.812 0 0 0 1.16 8z"/>
          <path d="M6.641 11.671V8.843h1.57l1.498 2.828h1.314L9.377 8.665c.897-.3 1.427-1.106 1.427-2.1 0-1.37-.943-2.246-2.456-2.246H5.5v7.352h1.141zm0-3.75V5.277h1.57c.881 0 1.416.499 1.416 1.32 0 .84-.504 1.324-1.386 1.324h-1.6z"/>
        </svg>
      
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Routine</h2>
        <p>Our pros create a new workout for you everyday and deliver it straight to your inbox. Get new insights and stay commited with a diverse selection of workouts and exercises.</p>
        <%= link_to "Try it out", home_modal_path,"data-controller": "turbo", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
